Query:
CREATE TABLE FOLDER_FOLDERNAME_ANALYSIS AS
-- EXPLAIN
SELECT F.id, F.path, FN.ratiobasisID FROM FOLDER F
	JOIN FOLDERNAME FN ON FN.name = F.name

SELECT A.*, RB.recommendedAction, RB.ratio, RB.weight FROM FOLDER_FOLDERNAME_ANALYSIS A
	JOIN RATIOBASIS RB ON A.ratiobasisID = RB.ID

CREATE TABLE FILE_FILENAME_ANALYSIS AS
-- EXPLAIN
SELECT F.id, F.name, F.folder, F.folderId, FN.ratiobasisID FROM FILE F
	JOIN FILENAME FN ON F.name = FN.name

SELECT A.*, RB.recommendedAction, RB.ratio, RB.weight FROM FILE_FILENAME_ANALYSIS A
	JOIN RATIOBASIS RB ON A.ratiobasisID = RB.ID

CREATE TABLE FILE_FOLDERNAME_ANALYSIS AS
-- EXPLAIN
SELECT F.id, F.name, F.folder, F.folderId, FN.ratiobasisID FROM FILE F
	JOIN FOLDER_FOLDERNAME_ANALYSIS FN ON F.folderID = FN.ID

SELECT A.*, RB.recommendedAction, RB.ratio, RB.weight FROM FILE_FOLDERNAME_ANALYSIS A
	JOIN RATIOBASIS RB ON A.ratiobasisID = RB.ID

CREATE TABLE FILE_FILETYPE_ANALYSIS AS
-- EXPLAIN
SELECT F.id, F.name, F.folder, F.filetype, FT.fileending as 'IDENTIFIED FILEENDING',  FT.ratiobasisID FROM FILE F
	JOIN FILETYPE FT ON F.filetype = FT.fileending

SELECT A.*, RB.recommendedAction, RB.ratio, RB.weight FROM FILE_FILETYPE_ANALYSIS A
	JOIN RATIOBASIS RB ON A.ratiobasisID = RB.ID
